| Vulnerability | Fix |
|---------------|-----|
| `java.util.Random` for security | Use `SecureRandom` instead |
| No cookie security attributes | Set HttpOnly, Secure, limit path |
| No input validation | Validate and sanitize all user input |
| Logging sensitive data | Avoid logging personal/security data |
| Predictable tokens | Use cryptographic random number generators |

